## 1. Comments

- `//` → Single-line comment  
- `/* … */` → Multi-line comment  
- `///` → Documentation comment  
- `/** … */` → Documentation comment (JavaDoc style)  
- Documentation comments تستخدم غالبًا مع **Public APIs**

